&lt;h2 id="section-tldr"&gt;Section TLDR&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The gauge is what allows you to use your most important actions. Do not overcap or overspend it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Damage or healing calculations occur when an action is cast, not when they apply to a target. This is important for buff optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;With GCD recast speeds faster than 2.50, you will occasionally (or always) use &lt;strong&gt;No Mercy&lt;/strong&gt; at 9 o-clock relative to the GCD roll indicator.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Gunbreaker&lt;/strong&gt; is a job with a focus on continuously building and spending cartridges to deal very high damage inside of strict burst windows. As a basic overview, the rotation is a builder-spender rotation focused on optimizing damage dealt every minute inside &lt;strong&gt;No Mercy&lt;/strong&gt;, which is a 20% damage buff that lasts for 20 seconds after its use.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Leveling Guide</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/tanks/gunbreaker/leveling-guide/</link><pubDate>Tue, 05 Aug 2025 20:49:45 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/tanks/gunbreaker/leveling-guide/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="intro"&gt;Intro&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This guide will teach you when to use your AOE skills while you are engaged in leveling content. You should generally follow these rules:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should be using &lt;strong&gt;No Mercy&lt;/strong&gt; off cooldown while in combat, unless doing so would waste most of it&amp;rsquo;s active duration (e.g. mobs during a dungeon pull have almost died.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You should be using all of your damaging off-GCD cooldowns such as &lt;strong&gt;Blasting Zone&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Bow Shock&lt;/strong&gt; on any number of enemies.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Best In Slot</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/tanks/gunbreaker/best-in-slot/</link><pubDate>Tue, 05 Aug 2025 20:49:16 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/tanks/gunbreaker/best-in-slot/</guid><description/></item><item><title>Advanced Guide</title><link>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/tanks/gunbreaker/advanced-guide/</link><pubDate>Mon, 26 Sep 2022 03:14:07 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.thebalanceffxiv.com/jobs/tanks/gunbreaker/advanced-guide/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Oops, we don&amp;rsquo;t have that guide yet! Interested in contributing? Feel free to join the &lt;a href="https://discord.gg/thebalanceffxiv"&gt;Balance Discord server&lt;/a&gt; to contact a job mentor/admin and express your interest!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>